<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=600" />
<title>财说证券交易账号绑定</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="padding-top:40px;font-family:微软雅黑;">
    <div style="padding-left:30px;padding-bottom:30px;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe1e0;margin-bottom:47px;"><img src="<%=Setting.html_host%>/images/mail-logo.png" /></div>
    <div style="padding-left:66px;width:70%;">
      <div style="min-width:600px;margin-bottom:40px;width:70%;background:#f4f6f8;padding:40px 30px 15px 40px;">
        <div style="color:#424458;font-size:14px;">
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">亲爱的财说用户,</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">我们收到你绑定证券交易账户的请求,请点击一下链接完成绑定：</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
            <a href="<%= pass_accounts_url(confirmation_token: @account.confirmation_token) %>" style="color:#64a0d7;font-size:14px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;">
              <%=pass_accounts_url(confirmation_token: @account.confirmation_token) %>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">这个链接24小时之后就会过期。</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">假如你没有发送该请求,请忽略该邮件。</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">谢谢！</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#424458;margin-top:76px;margin-bottom:100px;">财说团队</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
